items.title: UnitedHealth under criminal probe for possible Medicare fraud, WSJ reports
items.description: UnitedHealth said it had not been notified by the DOJ about the "supposed criminal investigation reported," and the company stood by "the integrity of our Medicare Advantage program."  The health insurer has been under pressure for months.
